This package uses Confix for all tasks related to building and installation.

For the uninformed, please read the Confix documentation at
http://confix.sf.net/. Then you will be informed ; kindly proceed to the
previous instruction.

For the informed, use the following :

o) Install the local component's environment:
   $ cd CCM_Local	
   $ confix.py --bootstrap --configure --make --targets="all install"

o) Install the remote component's environment:
   $ cd external
   $ confix.py --bootstrap --configure --make --targets="all install"
   $ cd CCM_Remote
   $ confix.py --bootstrap --configure --make --targets="all install"

o) Install the python component's environment:
   $ confix.py --packageroot=CCM_Python --bootstrap --configure --make --targets="all install"	
   But, it does not work because CCM_Python is the package root directory of the Python 
   generator environment!!	

For further questions, please consult the README file.
